# FitnessDuel Frontend Consistency

- Prefer existing shared UI primitives in `components/ui` before creating custom JSX or styling.
- Put reusable visual patterns in `components/ui`; keep feature-specific composition in feature folders.
- Do not hardcode user-visible strings in components; use translations from `app/[locale]/locales/fr.json`.
- Use semantic design tokens and existing variants instead of hardcoded colors or ad hoc visual classes.
- Preserve accessibility, responsive behavior, and interaction states when refactoring UI.
- Before finishing frontend work, verify shared UI consistency, translations, and basic lint/type safety.
